Interface BusinessRelationship

All Superinterfaces:
ModelObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
BusinessRelationshipImpl
public interface BusinessRelationship
extends ModelObject

A representation of the model object 'Business Relationship'.

The following features are supported:

  • Model
  • Source Table
  • Destination Table
  • Source Columns
  • Destination Columns
